gov.nih.nlm.ling.brat

Class AnnotationArgument

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.nih.nlm.ling.brat.AnnotationArgument
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<AnnotationArgument>

    public class AnnotationArgument
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<AnnotationArgument>
    Represents a role-argument pair of a more complex Annotation object (RelationAnnotation, EventAnnotation, etc.). A role is the function that the argument (participant) plays in the more complex semantic object, such as Theme, Agent for an EventAnnotation.
    Author:
    Halil Kilicoglu
